{"tid":818771,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"貪平出事了","createTime":"2018-09-14T10:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T03:14:57.000Z","uid":185175,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"43b9b97ea734ba97abd81db885a67648e6b2ce7c","tid":818771,"uid":185175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"小弟買左單程hk express 飛大阪，收到email話班機取消左。我第一次遇到呢啲事唔知點做，打客服又冇人聽，我應該買過張機票定係send email 話我想轉邊班機就得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下面係封email <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為配合您的行程安排，你可以考慮以下任何一個選項： <br />\n<br />\n1. 更改原定航線之出發日期，並於原定出發日期之兩個月內出發，需視乎機位供應情況而定。 <br />\n<br />\n或 <br />\n<br />\n2. 更改航線，並於原定出發日期之兩個月內出發，需視乎機位供應情況而定。 <br />\n<br />\n或 <br />\n<br />\n3. 退款安排：申請受影響之航班或訂單全數票價退款安排。您可透过 <a href=\"https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/e-refund/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecuresettlement.net%2Fhkexpress%2Fe-refund%2F&d=3yIU3YvVbR2hif99R5thy3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=62e6b77f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://securesettlement.net/hkexpress/e-refund/</a> 遞交您的退款申請。 <br />\n<br />\n選擇1或2安排之旅客皆可獲豁免票價差額及可享免費更改優惠一次；如需額外更改，旅客必須按照一般價格條款及細則繳付相關費用。有關安排須按機位供應而定及必須於原定出發日期前進行更改。另外，如欲進行上述選項(1)或(2)更改安排之旅客,你也可以先透<a href=\"https://booking.hkexpresss.com/預訂一個新的訂單，然後透過\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooking.hkexpresss.com%2F%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%BE%8C%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E&d=3yIU3YvVbR2hif99R5thy3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=0967afec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://booking.hkexpresss.com/預訂一個新的訂單，然後透過</a> <a href=\"https://www.securesettlement.net/hkexpress/e-refund/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.securesettlement.net%2Fhkexpress%2Fe-refund%2F&d=3yIU3YvVbR2hif99R5thy3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=871ee244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.securesettlement.net/hkexpress/e-refund/</a> 申請退款，所提交的退款申請必須符合我們的條款與細則。<br />\n<br />\n請注意：航班時刻表受航空公司控制條件的限制，可能會有所不同。<br />\n<br />\n查詢詳情，請透過網上留言 <a href=\"https://www.hkexpress.com/zh-hk/need-help/contact\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexpress.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fneed-help%2Fcontact&d=3yIU3YvVbR2hif99R5thy3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1783df4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkexpress.com/zh-hk/need-help/contact</a> 與我們聯絡，請聯同下列資料一併新起郵件發送至發送至guest.relations@hkexpress.com <br />\n<br />\n&bull; 上述航班選擇（請說明選擇新航班的建議 或 選項1、2 )<br />\n&bull; 訂單編號<br />\n&bull; 有效之聯絡電話"},{"pid":"c3380656af992a99b65dad8d2c2fdc7e909d5d6a","tid":818771,"uid":185175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:33:09.000Z","msg":"好撚驚 回程我又唔係買大阪返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736743206b8cd834ac9315aed7f2816428e6eac8","tid":818771,"uid":12463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"補錢轉地點"},{"pid":"c1fd12d4b65e0402b8a3288be812859b3bdd99aa","tid":818771,"uid":121562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"打電話，打幾個鐘就會有人聽"},{"pid":"f7432a491a625b3e5e8bf165b9915b95c6629fb1","tid":818771,"uid":185175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"我send左email去話轉地點 <br />\n我揀左選項2 <br />\n佢又冇覆 點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bc1af87249f6588e1b28e11c40ccb7a3a85f10","tid":818771,"uid":185175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"打電話 我打左好多次都係通話失敗"},{"pid":"2e7e32d24fb9aae4ef3e9bd21c380db7d6823365","tid":818771,"uid":128373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"上佢個官網 搵在線客服<br />\n唔好搵中文   唔會等到佢覆你<br />\n搵英文果班快好多  琴日已改機票"},{"pid":"077903a75c06a3d0b7fef2054def82ac877b40db","tid":818771,"uid":185175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e7e32d24fb